<p>
  {dgettext(
    "help_commands",
    "Manage server users: list, view details, ban, kick, mute, rename, assign roles, and run NickServ admin actions. The Admin Console Users tab provides command-backed list, search, banlist, Info, moderation, account, role, and NickServ controls. Requires server administrator role."
  )}
</p>

<.help_h4 icon={:icon_code}>{dgettext("help_commands", "Syntax")}</.help_h4>
<pre>{dgettext("help_commands", "/admin user list [--search Q] [--online] /admin user info @<nick> /admin user ban @<nick> [--reason R] [--duration D] /admin user unban @<nick> /admin user kick @<nick> [--reason R] /admin user mute @<nick> [--duration D] /admin user unmute @<nick> /admin user rename @<nick> <new_nick> /admin user role @<nick> <admin|server_operator|user> /admin user banlist [--search Q]")}</pre>

<.help_h4 icon={:icon_tag}>{dgettext("help_commands", "Subcommands")}</.help_h4>
<ul>
  <li>
    <code>list</code>
    {dgettext("help_commands", "— List registered users (filter with")} <code>--search</code>, <code>--online</code>)
  </li>
  <li>
    <code>info</code> {dgettext(
      "help_commands",
      "— Show detailed user info (registration, status, channels)"
    )}
  </li>
  <li>
    <code>ban</code>
    {dgettext("help_commands", "— Server ban (user cannot connect). Supports")} <code>{dgettext("help_commands", "--duration 1h")}</code>,
    <code>{dgettext("help_commands", "--reason text")}</code>
  </li>
  <li><code>unban</code> {dgettext("help_commands", "— Remove a server ban")}</li>
  <li>
    <code>kick</code> {dgettext(
      "help_commands",
      "— Force disconnect (user can reconnect immediately)"
    )}
  </li>
  <li>
    <code>mute</code>
    {dgettext("help_commands", "— Globally mute (cannot send messages anywhere). Supports")}
    <code>--duration</code>
  </li>
  <li><code>unmute</code> {dgettext("help_commands", "— Remove global mute")}</li>
  <li><code>rename</code> {dgettext("help_commands", "— Force nickname change")}</li>
  <li>
    <code>role</code>
    {dgettext("help_commands", "— Set server role:")} <code>admin</code>, <code>server_operator</code>{dgettext(
      "help_commands",
      ", or"
    )} <code>user</code>
    {dgettext("help_commands", "(removes role)")}
  </li>
  <li><code>banlist</code> {dgettext("help_commands", "— List active server bans")}</li>
</ul>

<.help_h4 icon={:icon_tab_nicklist}>
  {dgettext("help_commands", "Admin Console Users Tab")}
</.help_h4>
<p>
  {dgettext(
    "help_commands",
    "Open File → Admin Console, then choose Users to refresh /admin user list snapshots, apply search and online-only filters, inspect a nick with /admin user info, review /admin user banlist output, confirm ban/unban, kick, mute, or unmute actions, rename users, set server roles, and run /admin ns info/drop/resetpass without typing the commands."
  )}
</p>

<.help_h4 icon={:icon_rules}>{dgettext("help_commands", "Rules & Limits")}</.help_h4>
<ul>
  <li>{dgettext("help_commands", "Only root admins (env var) can promote users to admin")}</li>
  <li>
    {dgettext(
      "help_commands",
      "The Users tab disables the admin role choice unless the viewer is a configured root admin"
    )}
  </li>
  <li>{dgettext("help_commands", "Root admins cannot be demoted via commands")}</li>
  <li>{dgettext("help_commands", "All actions are recorded in the audit log")}</li>
  <li>
    {dgettext("help_commands", "Duration format:")} <code>30s</code>, <code>5m</code>, <code>1h</code>,
    <code>1d</code>
  </li>
</ul>

<.help_h4 icon={:icon_lightbulb}>{dgettext("help_commands", "Examples")}</.help_h4>
<pre>{dgettext("help_commands", "/admin user list --online /admin user ban @Spammer --reason Flooding --duration 24h /admin user kick @Troll --reason Breaking rules /admin user mute @Noisy --duration 30m /admin user role @Trusted server_operator")}</pre>

<.help_h4 icon={:icon_link}>{dgettext("help_commands", "See Also")}</.help_h4>
<p>
  <.help_link topic="cmd-admin">{dgettext("help_commands", "/admin")}</.help_link>
  ·
  <.help_link topic="feature-admin-console">
    {dgettext("help_commands", "Admin Console")}
  </.help_link>
  · <.help_link topic="cmd-kick">{dgettext("help_commands", "/kick")}</.help_link>
  · <.help_link topic="cmd-ban">{dgettext("help_commands", "/ban")}</.help_link>
  · <.help_link topic="cmd-mute">{dgettext("help_commands", "/mute")}</.help_link>
</p>
